{"tid":1739734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（和理非入 ）已經五個月啦 點解你地仲係唔識嗌（學術分享）","createTime":"2019-11-19T16:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T02:45:20.000Z","uid":61205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1dc5a06ea72aaa0d8179e00420bf1f800262ecca","tid":1739734,"uid":61205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:39:05.000Z","msg":"發夢聽到你地嗌得唔夠響. 唔夠震撼. 尤其是係快閃中環嗰班啊因為本身已經人少.<br />\nTempo係好重要. 嗌得太快會發唔到力. <br />\n用Fight for freedom黎做例子. 用接近或者慢過 戰狼300嘅 &ldquo;This is Spartar&rdquo; 黎嗌. （睇下面條片）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4Prc1UfuokY?t=124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4Prc1UfuokY%3Ft%3D124&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqP3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=4819ccce\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4Prc1UfuokY?t=124</a><br />\n<br />\n嗌之前吸氣要去到胸口漲起嘅程度. <br />\n先慢後快咁嗌. 每一個字之間有個小停頓比你運氣. (好多人都係頭幾個字好快跟住最尾個個字拉長）<br />\n之後其他人就跟住個tempo嗌第二句.<br />\n最好就係第一句有幾個人輪流嗌一次, 咁就唔會因為嗌幾下就要休息搞到冇人帶頭嗌而淨曬.<br />\n嗌口號唔係淨係bring out a message, 係要俾前線知道我地好多人支持佢哋, 係要擾亂黑警軍心.<br />\n<br />\n同埋之前有位玩聲樂嘅手足開過post教人點樣可以大聲啲 但係我搵唔返個post貼黎link."},{"pid":"bbd32515819a9dcfa43ab4b2bcfa77e2a17e0d9f","tid":1739734,"uid":61205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:40:50.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5b3476644640b51fb4baa10f84731da4671869d5","tid":1739734,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:43:12.000Z","msg":"星期六會有一個親子向嘅遊行，呼籲停止使用化學武器親子遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1739481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1739481</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"df2f8cc98f4935c4c4d6f08a0623d7ee93491c1a","tid":1739734,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1512603/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1512603/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c04f55ae34bd5de55f8c55fa03ddfbb8b9cf55e3","tid":1739734,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"